[{"text": "I'd like to start with a short story.", "start": 16.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "It's about a little boy", "start": 20.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "whose father was a history buff", "start": 22.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "and who used to take him by the hand", "start": 27.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to visit the ruins of an ancient metropolis", "start": 29.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "on the outskirts of their camp.", "start": 33.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They would always stop by to visit", "start": 36.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "these huge winged bulls that used to guard", "start": 39.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the gates of that ancient metropolis,", "start": 42.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the boy used to be scared", "start": 44.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of these winged bulls,", "start": 46.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but at the same time they excited him.", "start": 48.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the dad used to use those bulls", "start": 50.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to tell the boy stories about", "start": 52.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that civilization and their work.", "start": 54.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Let's fast-forward to the", "start": 58.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "San Francisco Bay Area many decades later,", "start": 61.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where I started a technology company", "start": 64.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that brought the world its first", "start": 67.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "3D laser scanning system.", "start": 70.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Let me show you how it works.", "start": 72.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Female Voice: Long range laser scanning", "start": 74.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by sending out a pulse that's a laser beam of light.", "start": 76.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The system measures the beam's time of flight,", "start": 79.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "recording the time it takes for the light", "start": 81.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to hit a surface and make its return.", "start": 83.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "With two mirrors, the scanner calculates", "start": 86.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the beam's horizontal and vertical angles,", "start": 88.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "giving accurate x, y, and z coordinates.", "start": 91.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The point is then recorded", "start": 94.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "into a 3D visualization program.", "start": 96.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "All of this happens in seconds.", "start": 101.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Ben Kacyra: You can see here,", "start": 106.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "these systems are extremely fast.", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They collect millions of points at a time", "start": 111.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with very high accuracy", "start": 114.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and very high resolution.", "start": 116.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A surveyor with traditional survey tools", "start": 118.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "would be hard-pressed to produce", "start": 121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "maybe 500 points in a whole day.", "start": 123.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These babies would be producing", "start": 126.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "something like ten thousand points a second.", "start": 129.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So, as you can imagine,", "start": 132.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this was a paradigm shift", "start": 134.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the survey and construction", "start": 137.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as well as in reality capture industry.", "start": 139.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Approximately ten years ago,", "start": 146.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my wife and I started a foundation to do good,", "start": 149.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and right about that time,", "start": 152.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the magnificent Bamiyan Buddhas,", "start": 154.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "hundred and eighty foot tall in Afghanistan,", "start": 157.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "were blown up by the Taliban.", "start": 160.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They were gone in an instant.", "start": 163.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And unfortunately, there was", "start": 165.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "no detailed documentation of these Buddhas.", "start": 167.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This clearly devastated me,", "start": 169.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I couldn't help but wonder about", "start": 171.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the fate of my old friends, the winged bulls,", "start": 173.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the fate of the many, many", "start": 176.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "heritage sites all over the world.", "start": 179.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Both my wife and I", "start": 182.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "were so touched by this", "start": 184.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we decided to", "start": 186.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "expand the mission of our foundation", "start": 188.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to include digital heritage preservation", "start": 191.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "of world sites.", "start": 195.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We called the project CyArk,", "start": 197.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which stands for Cyber Archive.", "start": 200.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "To date, with the help of", "start": 202.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a global network of partners,", "start": 204.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we've completed close to fifty projects.", "start": 207.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Let me show you some of them:", "start": 209.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Chichen Itza,", "start": 211.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Rapa Nui --", "start": 213.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and what you're seeing here", "start": 215.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are the cloud of points --", "start": 217.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Babylon,", "start": 219.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Rosslyn Chapel,", "start": 221.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Pompeii,", "start": 223.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and our latest project, Mt. Rushmore,", "start": 225.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which happened to be one of", "start": 227.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our most challenging projects.", "start": 229.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "As you see here, we had to develop", "start": 231.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a special rig to bring the scanner", "start": 233.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "up close and personal.", "start": 236.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The results of our work in the field", "start": 239.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are used to produce", "start": 242.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "media and deliverables to be used", "start": 244.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by conservators and researchers.", "start": 246.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We also produce media for", "start": 249.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "dissemination to the public --", "start": 253.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "free through the CyArk website.", "start": 256.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These would be used for education,", "start": 259.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "cultural tourism, etc.", "start": 262.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "What you're looking at in here", "start": 264.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is a 3D viewer that we developed", "start": 266.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that would allow the display", "start": 269.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and manipulation of [the] cloud of points", "start": 271.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in real time, cutting sections through them", "start": 273.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and extracting dimensions.", "start": 276.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This happens to be the cloud of points", "start": 278.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for Tikal.", "start": 280.26, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "In here you see a traditional 2D", "start": 281.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "architectural engineering drawing", "start": 283.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that's used for preservation, and of course", "start": 285.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we tell the stories through fly-throughs.", "start": 288.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And here, this is a fly-through", "start": 291.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the cloud of points of Tikal,", "start": 293.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and here you see it rendered", "start": 295.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and photo-textured with the photography", "start": 298.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we take of the site.", "start": 300.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And so this is not a video.", "start": 303.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is actual 3D points with", "start": 305.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "two to three millimeter accuracy.", "start": 307.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And of course the data can be used", "start": 311.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to develop 3D models that are", "start": 313.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "very accurate and very detailed.", "start": 316.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And here you're looking at a model", "start": 319.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that's extracted from the cloud of points", "start": 321.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for Stirling Castle.", "start": 323.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's used for studies, for visualization,", "start": 325.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as well as for education.", "start": 328.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And finally, we produce mobile apps", "start": 331.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that include narrated virtual tools.", "start": 333.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The more I got involved", "start": 337.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the heritage field,", "start": 340.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the more it became clear to me", "start": 342.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we are losing the sites", "start": 345.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the stories faster than we can", "start": 348.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "physically preserve them.", "start": 351.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Of course, earthquakes", "start": 354.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and all the natural phenomena --", "start": 356.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "floods, tornadoes, etc. --", "start": 358.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "take their toll.", "start": 360.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "However, what occurred to me was", "start": 363.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "human-caused destruction, which was", "start": 366.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not only causing a significant portion", "start": 368.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the destruction, but actually", "start": 370.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it was accelerating.", "start": 373.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This includes arson,", "start": 376.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "urban sprawl,", "start": 378.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "acid rain, not to mention", "start": 380.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "terrorism and wars.", "start": 383.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It was getting more and more apparent", "start": 385.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we're fighting a losing battle.", "start": 388.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We're losing our sites", "start": 390.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the stories,", "start": 392.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and basically we're losing", "start": 394.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a piece -- and a significant piece --", "start": 396.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of our collective memory.", "start": 398.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Imagine us as a human race", "start": 401.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not knowing where we came from.", "start": 403.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Luckily, in the last two or three decades,", "start": 407.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "digital technologies have been developing", "start": 410.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that have helped us to develop tools", "start": 413.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we've brought to bear", "start": 415.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the digital preservation,", "start": 417.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in our digital preservation war.", "start": 419.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This includes, for example,", "start": 421.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the 3D laser scanning systems,", "start": 423.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "ever more powerful personal computers,", "start": 427.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "3D graphics,", "start": 430.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "high-definition digital photography,", "start": 432.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not to mention the Internet.", "start": 435.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Because of this accelerated", "start": 438.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "pace of destruction,", "start": 440.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it became clear to us that we needed", "start": 442.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to challenge ourselves and our partners", "start": 444.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to accelerate our work.", "start": 447.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And we created a project", "start": 449.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we call the CyArk 500 Challenge --", "start": 451.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and that is to digitally preserve", "start": 454.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "500 World Heritage Sites", "start": 457.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in five years.", "start": 460.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We do have the technology", "start": 462.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that's scaleable,", "start": 464.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and our network of global partners", "start": 466.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "has been expanding and can be expanded", "start": 470.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "at a rapid rate,", "start": 473.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so we're comfortable", "start": 475.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that this task can be accomplished.", "start": 477.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "However, to me, the 500 is", "start": 480.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "really just the first 500.", "start": 483.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "In order to sustain our work into the future,", "start": 487.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "we use technology centers", "start": 491.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where we partner with", "start": 494.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "local universities and colleges", "start": 497.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to take the technology to them,", "start": 499.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "whereby they then can help us", "start": 502.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with digital preservation of their heritage sites,", "start": 505.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and at the same time, it gives them", "start": 508.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the technology to benefit from in the future.", "start": 511.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Let me close with another short story.", "start": 515.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Two years ago, we were approached", "start": 519.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by a partner of ours to digitally preserve", "start": 521.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "an important heritage site,", "start": 524.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a UNESCO heritage site in Uganda,", "start": 526.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the Royal Kasubi Tombs.", "start": 529.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The work was done successfully in the field,", "start": 532.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the data was archived", "start": 535.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and publicly disseminated", "start": 537.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "through the CyArk website.", "start": 539.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Last March,", "start": 542.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we received very sad news.", "start": 544.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The Royal Tombs had been destroyed", "start": 547.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "by suspected arson.", "start": 550.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A few days later, we received a call:", "start": 553.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "\"Is the data available", "start": 556.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and can it be used for reconstruction?\"", "start": 559.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Our answer, of course, was yes.", "start": 563.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Let me leave you with a final thought.", "start": 568.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Our heritage is much more than", "start": 571.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "our collective memory --", "start": 574.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it's our collective treasure.", "start": 576.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We owe it to our children,", "start": 578.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "our grandchildren and the generations", "start": 581.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we will never meet", "start": 583.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to keep it safe", "start": 586.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and to pass it along.", "start": 588.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 590.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 592.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 594.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 596.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 598.26, "duration": 11.0}, {"text": "Well, I'm staying here because", "start": 609.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "we wanted to demonstrate to you", "start": 613.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the power of this technology", "start": 616.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and so, while I've been speaking,", "start": 619.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you have been scanned.", "start": 622.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 625.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The two wizards that I have", "start": 629.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that are behind the curtain", "start": 632.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "will help me bring", "start": 634.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the results on the screen.", "start": 637.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 645.26, "duration": 7.0}, {"text": "This is all in 3D and of course", "start": 652.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you can fly through the cloud of points.", "start": 655.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You can look at it from on top,", "start": 658.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from the ceiling.", "start": 660.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You can look from different vantage points,", "start": 662.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I'm going to ask Doug to zoom in", "start": 664.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on an individual in the crowd,", "start": 667.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "just to show the amount of detail", "start": 670.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we can create.", "start": 673.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So you have been digitally preserved", "start": 679.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in about four minutes.", "start": 682.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 684.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'd like to thank the wizards here.", "start": 686.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "We were very lucky to have", "start": 690.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "two of our partners participate in this:", "start": 693.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "the Historic Scotland,", "start": 697.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the Glasgow School of Art.", "start": 699.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'd like to also thank personally", "start": 702.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "the efforts of David Mitchell,", "start": 706.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "who is the Director of Conservation", "start": 710.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "at Historic Scotland.", "start": 713.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "David.", "start": 715.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 717.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And Doug Pritchard, who's the Head of", "start": 722.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Visualization at the Glasgow School of Art.", "start": 724.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Let's give them a hand.", "start": 727.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 729.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 732.26, "duration": 3.0}]